title: Open Weekends For Tour-Newly Renovated-Luxury Amenities-Great Location
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
